3.00	Mayhem_on_Bear_Creek	Mayhem on Bear Creek	Mayhem on Bear Creek is a collection of Western short stories by Robert E. Howard. It was first published in 1979 by Donald M. Grant, Publisher, Inc. in an edition of 1,900 copies. The stories had not previously been collected.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/e/ef/Mayhem_on_bear_creek.jpg
